Content:: The 2019 Tour de Romandie was a road cycling stage race, that took place between 30 April and 5 May 2019 in Switzerland. It was the 73rd edition of the Tour de Romandie and the 21st race of the 2019 UCI World Tour.[1] In total, twenty teams start the race. Each team delivered seven riders.[2] UCI WorldTeams UCI Professional Continental teams National teams
